title: The Worst (and Best) Golf Club Logos
headline: The Worst (and Best) Golf Club Logos
description: Bad golf logos are everywhere, marring otherwise perfectly good shirts and ball markers around the world. The offenders fall into one of four categories: (1) Animals, (2) Trees, (3) Crests and (4) WTF? Let’s examine each for examples of the insipid, and the inspired.
